Title: Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy
Plot: SpongeBob and Patrick try to meet the stars of their favorite superhero series, "Mermaid Man and Barnacle Boy", who currently reside in the local rest home.
Director: Alan Smart, Walt Dohrn, Sherm Cohen
Writer: Paul Tibbitt, Mark O'Hare, Doug Lawrence
GuestStars: Ernest Borgnine (Mermaid Man), Tim Conway (Barnacle Boy)
